<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Meeting Completed</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #45a049); padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">üéâ Meeting Completed!</h1>
    </div>
    <div
      style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
    >
      <p>Hello {{menteeName}},</p>
      <p>Your mentorship session with <strong>{{mentorName}}</strong> has been successfully completed!</p>

      <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h2 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-top: 0;">Session Summary</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Mentor:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{mentorName}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Plan:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{planType}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Date:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{meetingDate}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Time:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{startTime}} - {{endTime}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Status:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold;">‚úì Completed</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: #E8F5E9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;"
      >
        <h3 style="color: #2E7D32; margin-top: 0;">üìù Share Your Experience</h3>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0; color: #1B5E20;">
          We'd love to hear about your mentorship experience! Your feedback helps us improve and helps other mentees
          make informed decisions.
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0; color: #1B5E20;">
          Please take a moment to rate your session and share your thoughts about working with
          {{mentorName}}.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
        <a
          href="{{feedbackUrl}}"
          style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;"
        >
          Leave Feedback
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: #FFF9C4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #FBC02D;"
      >
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #F57F17;">
          <strong>üí° Tip:</strong>
          Continue your learning journey by booking another session or exploring other mentors on Mentoria!
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for choosing Mentoria for your mentorship needs!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />The Mentoria Team</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 0.8em;">
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>